Step 1 :
Run a Nubit light node with a simple command.

curl -sL1 https://nubit.sh | bash

Step 2 :
Save your Nubit light node pubkey.
a. Each time you run the command, your light node pubkey will be printed out. Make sure to save it securely.


Step 3 :
Verify your Nubit light node pubkey after 15 minutes.
a. Once the light node is started, wait about 15 minutes before returning to claim your light node reward.
b. Copy and paste your light node pubkey into the provided field and click “Verify.”
c. If your pubkey passes verification, your account will receive 3000 points immediately.
d. Note that each pubkey can be verified only once, and each account can receive the 3000 points bonus only once.
